query:
SELECT productId, partNumber, name, 
  LENGTH(description) as desc_length,
  particleSize, poreSize, columnLength, innerDiameter
FROM products 
WHERE brand = 'Agilent'
AND partNumber NOT IN ('959993-902', '959757-902', '821125-936', '959961-302', '821725-901', '959941-902', '880952-704', '880952-706', '880952-705')
LIMIT 10
